column8:
> I DO RECOMMEND THIS GAME, JUST NOT THIS VERSION <

Pros:
 - great characters and GF models/mugshots (except the freaking PROTAGONIST face/hair);
 - stable FPS after last patch;
 - some parts that weren't speedable in original PC release now can be accelerated;

Cons:
 - Squall hair/face makes him looks more like a Barbie-like Ken doll than a freaking Seed/mercenary;
 - backgrounds are blurry then ever;
 - PS1 features still missing (analog controller, vibration and correct audio on opening FMV);
 - widescreen removed;

=======
Original PC release with all graphic mods possible still way better (if Squall/Rinoah models receive a mod to be more FMV-like on the remaster maybe I change to this version)

